  "title": "Content Creator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company</strong></p>\n<p>Cintra Consultancy is a full-stack social media agency based in Singapore helping brands scale with platform-native content and performance creative.</p>\n<p><strong>Role Overview</strong><br>\nWe’re on the lookout for a <strong>Content Creator</strong> to spearhead social growth strategies and create organic content for our clients. We create graphics, videos like skits and street interviews for our clients. A secondary part of your role will involve conceptualising and producing content for Cintra’s own social presence.</p>\n<h3>What You’ll Do</h3>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support the ideation and development of content strategies for our clients</li>\n  <li>Create and produce social media content, from brainstorming video concepts to leading shoots</li>\n  <li>Ideate and create engaging videos, graphics and stories for our clients</li>\n  <li>Manage and think of engaging ideas that will help the client's social media account grow</li>\n  <li>Edit and produce high-quality short-form videos tailored for TikTok and Meta</li>\n  <li>Content creation, and asset development for Cintra’s in-house marketing</li>\n  <li>Ensure every output for TikTok and Instagram is intentional, sharp, and scroll-stopping.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Up-to-date with current social media trends, viral formats, and editing styles</li>\n  <li>Have prior experience in short-form video editing, particularly for TikTok &amp; IG Reels</li>\n  <li>Adaptable and comfortable working in a fast-moving environment</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience creating content, filming, scripting, editing, on an iPhone or GoPro</li>\n  <li>Bonus points if you’ve done skits, POV content, or street interviews before</li>\n  <li>Bonus: Experience with Adobe Premiere, CapCut and Adobe After Effects</li>\n</ul>",
